Package: smaR
Title: "Simple Metagenomic Analysis in R"
Year: 2024
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(  person("Niccolo", "Carlino", email = "carlino.nicc@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment=c(ORCID="0009-0004-7409-449X")))
Depends: R (>= 4.4)
Description: smaR (Simple Metagenomic Analyses in R) provides a set of tools for basic metagenomic analyses. Starting from merged
    taxonomic profiles and a metadata table, it centralizes function for data checks, alpha- and beta-diversity analysis, differential abundance
    analysis and visualization. The package aims to simplify and homogenize common workflows.
